OL,4,CCovid bubbles to be axed in England's
OL,5,Cschools
OL,6, Covid rules that have seen hundreds of
OL,7, thousands of pupils miss out on
OL,8, learning due to self-isolation are
OL,9, being axed in England, it is confirmed.
OL,11,FEducation Secretary Gavin Williamson
OL,12,Fsaid the system of sending "bubbles" of
OL,13,Fchildren home after a positive case
OL,14,Fwould cease at the end of summer term.
OL,16,FThe bubble system had been necessary to
OL,17,Flimit virus spread but was now causing
OL,18,Fdisruption to pupils' lives, he said.
OL,20,FTeaching unions warned against easing
OL,21,Frules as cases are still rising.
